UPDATES
This section includes new information about Zortech C++ that wasn't 
included in the manuals.


The Developer's Edition

The manuals refer to the version of Zortech C++ that does not contain the
Numerics Programming Guide or the M++ Library as the Developer's Edition. 
That's the old name of that version. It is now called, simply, Zortech C++. 
The version that does contain the Numerics Programming Guide and the M++
Class Library is still called the Engineering and Science Edition.
